{"tid":2413022,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兩隻貓相處求教","createTime":"2021-02-18T11:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T22:50:25.000Z","uid":93599,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0b47452722b6c98edf19a7c7f5e5639d0e178f31","tid":2413022,"uid":93599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:17:32.000Z","msg":"話說我兩隻貓同時喺領養中心領養返嚟<br />\nA貓大過B貓兩個月<br />\n一直都有玩 有打交<br />\n一直都好friend<br />\n但唔會話邊個驚邊個<br />\n<br />\n上個月我拎完佢地同時去絕育<br />\n絕育完返到嚟<br />\nB貓成日打到A貓要避佢 好驚<br />\n而且係要驚到A貓要fee B貓嘅級數（絕育前從未發生過要fee對方）<br />\n<br />\n我好唔好由而家開始將佢地分開瞓？（因為依家屋企無人就會困佢地同房）<br />\n有人在場先放返佢哋出嚟一齊？<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9f083c4aa98bbe64542e1e3ff2d9dbe178f600","tid":2413022,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"有人醒先開放<br />\n無人就分隔"},{"pid":"3aeffe415a4eeb09b1c72ff3560ac18ee746dc40","tid":2413022,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dd7efc6d501dbca39b4d7389b11dab17225b3d","tid":2413022,"uid":174763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"俾人閹咗，雄風盡失，係會頹啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（貓咪絕育後性情大變屬於正常情況，但係如果性格變得好奇怪，要睇下會唔會係患上咗心理疾病"},{"pid":"7ae994dc6169e28f1aeb825495c3bd27017bf93f","tid":2413022,"uid":93599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29dd7efc6d501dbca39b4d7389b11dab17225b3d","tid":2413022,"uid":174763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"俾人閹咗，雄風盡失，係會頹啲嘅<im